            We value quality over quantity. Tell us about yourself and why you'd be a great fit for Elism.
          </p>
        </div>

        <form onSubmit={handleSubmit} className="space-y-10">
          <div className="glass p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 space-y-8">
            <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              <div className="space-y-2">
                <label className="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-wider">How old are you?</label>
